class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92d878137b9567ade62862b847b79c9e848a7f8","tid":1737092,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb4413ff27662a9449e3677835eeb4be3168c2c","tid":1737092,"uid":312332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:46:41.000Z","msg":"連儂牆：絕對係 50歲以上人士既資訊來源<br />\n<br />\n無連儂牆後果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無左連儂牆，佢地只會返去睇CCTVB</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">1：連儂牆位置分主區及副區</span></span><br />\n主區： 圖片要美化，排列要工整<br />\n副區：屬於隨時陣亡/被清洗區，唔洗太靚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆急需擴展<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>建議找尋真黃店，借佢半邊外牆興建連儂牆，記得要美圖，仲要好聲好氣問，可以拒絕</em></span><br />\n~借用位置不得高於一半，否則影響店舖透光<br />\n~借用大細可長可短，壁報板大細都可以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">變相成為驗證真真真黃店!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做人要有禮貌，拒絕唔代表對方藍</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最重要係內容</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家更改連儂牆內容<br />\n<br />\n警暴是果，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">貪腐政權是因</span><br />\n<br />\n我發現大家由6月反修例開始，比政府spin到去黑社會，再由黑社會spin到去警暴<br />\n<br />\n但係最終源頭，都係政權貪腐，勾結黑幫，包庇警暴，係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">官鄉警黑勾結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆一定要 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Post大量政權貪污資訊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人一定要打岩政治旗號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反貪污</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反黑社會</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反警暴</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">打黑反貪，反官鄉警黑勾結</span></span>"},{"pid":"679a187cb574bd3ad60363087fe550c6bce9be8d","tid":1737092,"uid":198958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bdda7f1ce4e82b0f405668b58d21249a0fab100","tid":1737092,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"波蘭connect 波蘭妹靚唔靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\n<br />\n我條女係波蘭人"},{"pid":"9d81ab2a167f57004aa4e654ca1768353cb2895e","tid":1737092,"uid":320978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n街坊落街宵夜注意事項<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724246</a>"}]}